headline: KeyBank Heritage Center Opens to Celebrate Bank's Bicentennial and Commitment to Communities it Serves
summary: Today, as part of its bicentennial celebration, KeyBank (NYSE: KEY) held a grand opening at its new Heritage Center in Cleveland. As part of the celebration, KeyCorp Chairman and CEO Chris Gorman took part in a ribbon cutting with Key teammates and local dignitaries.
